Name: James Milner
Number: 7
Position: Midfielder
Goals: 26
Assists: 86

James Milner’s five full seasons with Liverpool have yielded four major trophies: 
the Premier League, Champions League, FIFA Club World Cup and UEFA Super Cup.
Appointed vice-captain upon his arrival from a successful stint with Manchester City 
in the summer of 2015, Milner’s leadership, experience, professionalism and versatility 
make him an integral member of Jürgen Klopp’s squad.

